# OpenAPI Generator keep-list (.openapi-generator-ignore).
#
# Patterns follow .gitignore syntax with last-match-wins semantics, so order
# matters: a later pattern overrides an earlier one. `prune` (see Makefile)
# deletes any tracked file the generator no longer emits unless it is kept here.
# Sections are alphabetised within themselves; the one exception is the auth
# negation block, whose `!` re-includes must stay immediately after the broad
# `src/auth/**` keep (moving them ahead would flip which files are regenerated).

# --- bespoke authenticators (ported onto the generated auth interfaces) ---
# The generator owns only the auth scaffolding (the `Authenticator` interface,
# `BaseAuthenticator`, `BearerAuthenticator`, `HttpAwareAuthenticator`). Every
# concrete Zitadel authenticator plus the auth barrel is hand-maintained, so
# keep the whole directory, then re-enable overwriting for the four scaffolding
# files. The broad keep MUST stay first; its `!` exceptions follow it.
src/auth/**
!src/auth/authenticator.ts
!src/auth/base-authenticator.ts
!src/auth/bearer-authenticator.ts
!src/auth/http-aware-authenticator.ts

# --- bespoke support classes (facade + back-compat error shims + helpers the generator does not emit) ---
# `src/zitadel.ts` is the public Zitadel facade and `src/index.ts` the barrel
# that re-exports it as the package default. `api-exception.ts` /
# `zitadel-exception.ts` re-export the generated typed `ApiError` under the
# `ApiException` / `ZitadelException` names the integration specs import.
src/api-exception.ts
src/index.ts
src/zitadel-exception.ts
src/zitadel.ts

# --- bespoke tests + fixtures the generator does not emit ---
# Integration specs, their Zitadel server fixtures, and the hand-authored unit
# tests (public facade, ApiException shim, the Zitadel authenticators). The
# spec-independent unit tests are generator-owned and intentionally absent.
etc/
spec/
test/api-exception.test.ts
test/auth/client-credentials-authenticator.test.ts
test/auth/no-auth-authenticator.test.ts
test/auth/oauth-authenticator-test.ts
test/auth/personal-access-authenticator.test.ts
test/auth/web-token-authenticator.test.ts
test/fixtures/
test/index.test.ts
test/setup.js

