VERSIONING.md

# --- house tooling (team-owned) ---
# Lint/format configs carry the generator's defaults verbatim (ESLint flat =
# `@eslint/js` + `typescript-eslint` recommended; Prettier = defaults). The only
# deviation is the ESM filename, since the package is `"type": "module"`; the
# CommonJS variants (`eslint.config.js`, `.prettierrc.json`) are kept so a regen
# cannot shadow the ESM config the package actually loads.
.dockerignore
.editorconfig
.github/
.gitignore
.idea/
.npmrc
.nvmrc
.pre-commit-config.yaml
.prettierignore
.prettierrc.json
.run/
